<title>USA: FiberCore Inc Q1 shr loss widens.</title>
<headline>FiberCore Inc Q1 shr loss widens.</headline>
<dateline>STURBRIDGE, Mass. 1997-05-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Following are the results of operations for the three months ended March 31:</p>
<p>							  ($000)</p>
<p>						  1997	   1996</p>
<p>Sales					 $2,000	  $1,970</p>
<p>Gross Profit				$  285	  $   68</p>
<p>Net Loss				    $ (953)	 $(718)</p>
<p>Loss per share			    $(0.03)	 $(0.02)</p>
<p>NOTE: Contributing to the increased loss was an increase in interest expense on loans for the expansion of the German facility, and an increase in research and development expenditures.</p>
<p>The company said the relatively small increase in sales was affected by the decline in value of the mark. -- New York Newsdesk</p>
